data.description: Welcome to beautiful Spring Grove Plantation!  This gem of a home effortlessly combines both style and comfort, offering 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 and a half baths. Situated on a serene cul-de-sac, this property sets the standard for Lowcountry living. From the moment you arrive, the home's alluring curb appeal invites you in, capturing the essence of Southern elegance. Step into a bright, open-concept layout where natural light dances across hardwood floors that grace the downstairs. You'll be immediately drawn in by the most popular floorplan that offers a large kitchen island looking towars the living room, a perfect setting for gathering and relaxation.The kitchen is a culinary dream, boasting an array of stainless-steel appliances including a gas range for expert level meal preparation. The granite countertops not only add a touch of luxury but also offer durability and practicality. The ample kitchen space is both functional and aesthetically pleasing, ensuring that dinner time becomes an experience to look forward to.  Retire to the Owner's suite, where tranquility awaits. The deluxe primary bath has been designed with relaxation in mind, featuring a separate shower, a luxurious garden tub, and dual vanity sinks.  Additional bedrooms are generously sized and perfect for family, guests, or even a home office. Each room offers plenty of storage, creating practical yet elegant living spaces. The home also features a screened-in porch, overlooking a fully fenced backyard, a quintessential space for outdoor entertaining or peaceful solitude.  Larger driveway and 2 car garage allow you to easily park vehicles when arriving home!  As a resident of this outstanding community, you'll enjoy many amenities including a community pool, play park, a frisbee golf course, and walking trails. Plus, you'll be conveniently located near shopping, dining, and major roadways, making this home the perfect fusion of luxury and convenience.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary property your new home. Schedule your private tour today!
